					        			<div class="row" style="margin-top:0;">
                        <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-12" style="position:relative;">
                            <img src="http://www.livemint.com/rf/Image-621x414/LiveMint/Period1/2015/08/01/Photos/cricket-kSR--621x414@LiveMint.jpg" alt="India-Pakistan cricket: Don't let the maniacs play spoilsport" title="India-Pakistan cricket: Don't let the maniacs play spoilsport" class="img-responsive" >
                            <div class="headlineContainer text-center">
                                <h1>India-Pakistan cricket: Don't let the maniacs play spoilsport</h1>
                            </div>
                        </div>
						<div class = "clearfix"></div>
                         <div class="col-lg-12">
                             <p class="credit pa15 text-right">Photo: Reuters</p>
                             <p class="intro pa15" style="margin-bottom:0;">When relations between the two nations are not held hostage by terror, the contest has always produced magic</p>
                         </div>
                    </div>
                    
					
                    <div class="row pa15 text-center">
                        <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-12 col-lg-12 socialIons">
